## Quality Gates
- [ ] Integration tests with exchange sandbox APIs
- [ ] WebSocket reconnection tested (disconnect simulation)
- [ ] Rate limiter prevents violations (load testing)
- [ ] All exchange quirks documented and handled
- [ ] Error scenarios tested and logged

## Success Criteria
- Zero rate limit violations in production
- <5 second WebSocket reconnection
- >99.9% connection uptime
- 100% order precision compliance

**Contract Status**: Active
**Review Frequency**: Weekly during implementation
